    "is_good_patch": true,
    "synth_pr": "\n## Title: Fix buffer over-read in NAS IE decode functions\n\n### Summary\nAdded buffer length checks in decode functions for various NAS Information Elements to prevent buffer over-read vulnerabilities when parsing TLV-formatted IEs.\n\n### Changes\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/MsNetworkCapability.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/AuthenticationFailureParameter.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field  \n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/EsmMessageContainer.c`: Added buffer length check before reading 16-bit length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/NetworkName.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/MobileStationClassmark2.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/VoiceDomainPreferenceAndUeUsageSetting.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/UeSecurityCapability.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/PlmnList.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/Cli.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/PdnAddress.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/NasMessageContainer.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/AuthenticationParameterAutn.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/AccessPointName.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/EpsBearerContextStatus.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/ApnAggregateMaximumBitRate.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/AuthenticationResponseParameter.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/DaylightSavingTime.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/EmergencyNumberList.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/EpsMobileIdentity.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/EpsNetworkFeatureSupport.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/EpsQualityOfService.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/LcsClientIdentity.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/MobileIdentity.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/PacketFlowIdentifier.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/ProtocolConfigurationOptions.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/QualityOfService.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/SupportedCodecList.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/TrackingAreaIdentityList.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n- `openair3/NAS/COMMON/IES/TrafficFlowTemplate.c`: Added buffer length check before reading length field\n\n"
